org.battlenight.api.command
Class BattleNightCommand

java.lang.Object
  org.battlenight.api.command.BattleNightCommand

public abstract class BattleNightCommand
extends Object

Represents a BattleNight sub-command. For it to be effective it needs to be registered with the CommandManager.
